{"tid":1007944,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(高慶坊) 冇沒人唔鋤大Dee 轉鋤uno","createTime":"2019-02-04T06:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T06:41:35.000Z","uid":144735,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e9701ff7166180f615a9729aabd5799ccf3700ee","tid":1007944,"uid":144735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T06:29:57.000Z","msg":"基本同uno一樣玩法，人數四人。<br />\n是但一個結牌就即刻計數：<br />\n數目牌 0 - 9 (手牌上所有點數相加)<br />\nFunction 牌 = 每張10點。<br />\nDraw 2 / Draw 4 = 成手牌點數 x 2 / x 4 <br />\n<br />\nexample = <br />\n&quot;0&quot; &quot;3&quot; &quot;7&quot; &quot;5&quot; &quot;9&quot; &quot;4&quot; &quot;skip&quot; &quot;reverse&quot; &quot;draw 2&quot; &quot;draw 4&quot;<br />\n計法:<br />\n(0+3+7+5+9+4+10+10) x 2 x 4 = total 384點<br />\n係唔係益智過鋤dee"},{"pid":"13e81ac6a88322d0b2c8e0fbd3b89ae8ba9475d9","tid":1007944,"uid":56610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T06:36:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>冇沒錢買啤牌?</strong></span>"},{"pid":"31cf9b265417c12135ef713533e9e813eb6fb512","tid":1007944,"uid":144735,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T06:41:35.000Z","msg":"鋤dee都可以俾上家夾三炒，呢個都可以用 cut / function 卡自救。"}]}